How to run oozie workflow with hive action

1. Copy workflow.xml, job.properties and script.q to your working directory.

2. Modify job.properties & script.q as per your cluster environment.

3. Put workflow.xml and script.q on hdfs at ${oozie.wf.application.path} given in job.properties file

4. Submit oozie workflow using below command

oozie job -oozie http://<oozie-server>:11000/oozie -config $working_dir/job.properties -run


Please visit http://crazyadmins.com for cool hadoop stuff!


Thank you!! Happy Hadooping :-)
